# Per-job remediation runtime artifacts (worker prompt, last-message,
# reply JSON, logs). These are generated each round and must never be
# committed; a stale snapshot leaks PR-specific state into the repo
# (e.g. PR #15 remediation-reply.json was carried as a tracked file
# until PR #127's round-2 review flagged it as drift).
